name: Whiskas Adult Ocean Fish Food
description: Whiskas ocean fish provides 100% complete and balanced nutrition for your adult cat. It contains tasty filled pocket kibbles – crunchy on the outside with a soft and delicious centre. The specially designed kibble provides a gentle abrasive effect to help clean your cat’s teeth and support healthy gums. With delicious high quality ocean fish ingredients, whiskas ocean fish dry food for adult cats is a great tasting way to help ensure your pet has all the necessary nutrients needed to grow healthy & strong. Help your cat grow healthy and strong with whiskas ocean fish. *Images for illustration purposes only. Product received may vary.
